---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import Breadcrumb from "../components/Breadcrumb.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Contact Us | Free Website Quote | doticrosst"
  description="Get in touch with doticrosst. Request a free website quote or send us a message about your project."
>
  <!-- Page header -->
  <section class="bg-charcoal py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <Breadcrumb
        items={[
          { label: "Home", href: "/" },
          { label: "Contact" },
        ]}
      />
      <div class="mt-4 max-w-2xl">
        <p class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-accent-light">Contact</p>
        <h1 class="mt-3 text-4xl font-black text-white sm:text-5xl">Contact us for a free website quote</h1>
        <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-300">
          Whether you've got a specific project in mind or just want to
          explore your options, we'd love to hear from you.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-white py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-16 lg:grid-cols-5">
        <!-- Info -->
        <div class="lg:col-span-2">
          <div class="space-y-8">
            <div>
              <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-charcoal">Get your free website quote</h2>
              <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-500">
                Use the form on this page to tell us about your project, or email us directly.
                We respond to every enquiry within one working day with a clear, no-obligation
                quote. No chasing, no hard sell -- just an honest conversation about what your
                business needs and what it will cost.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h2 class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-gray-400">Email</h2>
              <a href="mailto:craig@doticrosst.com" class="mt-2 block text-lg font-semibold text-accent transition-colors duration-200 hover:text-accent-light">
                craig@doticrosst.com
              </a>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h2 class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-gray-400">Response time</h2>
              <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600">Usually within 24 hours</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h2 class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-gray-400">No obligation</h2>
              <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-500">
                Every conversation starts with listening. No hard sell, no pressure.
                If we're not the right fit, we'll tell you.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Form -->
        <div class="lg:col-span-3">
          <form
            class="rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 bg-gray-50 p-8 shadow-sm"
            name="contact"
            method="POST"
            data-netlify="true"
            netlify-honeypot="bot-field"
          >
            <input type="hidden" name="form-name" value="contact" />
            <p class="hidden" aria-hidden="true">
              <label>Don't fill this out: <input name="bot-field" tabindex="-1" /></label>
            </p>

            <div class="space-y-5">
              <div>
                <label for="name" class="mb-1.5 block text-sm font-medium text-charcoal">Name</label>
                <input
                  type="text"
                  id="name"
                  name="name"
                  required
                  autocomplete="name"
                  class="w-full rounded-lg border border-gray-200 bg-white px-4 py-3 text-sm text-charcoal transition-all duration-200 placeholder:text-gray-400 focus:border-accent focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-accent/20"
                />
              </div>

              <div>
                <label for="email" class="mb-1.5 block text-sm font-medium text-charcoal">Email</label>
                <input
                  type="email"
                  id="email"
                  name="email"
                  required
                  autocomplete="email"
                  class="w-full rounded-lg border border-gray-200 bg-white px-4 py-3 text-sm text-charcoal transition-all duration-200 placeholder:text-gray-400 focus:border-accent focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-accent/20"
                />
              </div>

              <div>
                <label for="business" class="mb-1.5 block text-sm font-medium text-charcoal">Business name (optional)</label>
                <input
                  type="text"
                  id="business"
                  name="business"
                  class="w-full rounded-lg border border-gray-200 bg-white px-4 py-3 text-sm text-charcoal transition-all duration-200 placeholder:text-gray-400 focus:border-accent focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-accent/20"
                />
              </div>

              <div>
                <label for="service" class="mb-1.5 block text-sm font-medium text-charcoal">What are you interested in?</label>
                <select
                  id="service"
                  name="service"
                  class="w-full rounded-lg border border-gray-200 bg-white px-4 py-3 text-sm text-charcoal transition-all duration-200 focus:border-accent focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-accent/20"
                >
                  <option value="">Select a service...</option>
                  <option value="booking-system">Booking System</option>
                  <option value="website-seo">Website & SEO</option>
                  <option value="automation">API Workflows & Automation</option>
                  <option value="not-sure">Not sure yet</option>
                </select>
              </div>

              <div>
                <label for="message" class="mb-1.5 block text-sm font-medium text-charcoal">Tell us about your project</label>
                <textarea
                  id="message"
                  name="message"
                  rows="5"
                  required
                  class="w-full resize-y rounded-lg border border-gray-200 bg-white px-4 py-3 text-sm text-charcoal transition-all duration-200 placeholder:text-gray-400 focus:border-accent focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-accent/20"
                ></textarea>
              </div>

              <button
                type="submit"
                class="w-full rounded-lg bg-accent px-6 py-3.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white transition-all duration-200 hover:bg-accent-light hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-accent/25"
              >
                Send Message
              </button>
            </div>
          </form>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What happens next -->
  <section class="bg-gray-50 py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-charcoal">What happens after you contact us</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 leading-relaxed text-gray-500">
          Once you send your message or fill in our scoping form, here is what to expect.
          We will review your enquiry and come back to you within one working day. That
          response will include our initial thoughts on scope, a ballpark quote if we have
          enough information, and any questions we need answered before moving forward.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4 leading-relaxed text-gray-500">
          If it makes sense, we will arrange a short call to go through the details. These
          calls are relaxed and practical -- no slides, no corporate presentations. We talk
          through what your business needs, what your website should do, and how we would
          build it. Most calls last 15 to 20 minutes.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4 leading-relaxed text-gray-500">
          After that call, you will receive a clear written quote with a fixed price. No
          hidden extras, no hourly billing that spirals. You know exactly what you are
          getting and what it costs before any work begins. If you decide to go ahead,
          your website is typically live within two to three weeks.
        </p>

        <h2 class="mt-12 text-2xl font-black text-charcoal">Who is this for?</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 leading-relaxed text-gray-500">
          We work with small businesses across the UK. If you are a hairdresser, barber,
          tradesperson, consultant, or any other small business owner who needs a website
          that actually brings in customers, we would like to hear from you. Whether you
          need a new website from scratch, a rebuild of an existing site, or help with
          local SEO to get more visibility on Google, contact us and we will give you a
          straight answer about what we can do.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4 leading-relaxed text-gray-500">
          We are equally happy to work with businesses that have no existing website and
          those who have an underperforming site they want replaced. Our free website quote
          covers everything -- design, build, local SEO setup, and ongoing support options.
          There is no obligation to proceed after receiving your quote.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<script>
  const form = document.querySelector("form") as HTMLFormElement;
  const btn = form?.querySelector("button[type=submit]") as HTMLButtonElement;

  form?.addEventListener("submit", () => {
    btn.disabled = true;
    btn.textContent = "Sending...";
  });
</script>
